      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and represents the absolute best-maintained example you will find. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear whatsoever. Mechanically, it performs exactly as it did the day it left the factory, with every feature functioning perfectly. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been meticulously cared for and preserved in top-tier condition.",
