    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable set of wheels that won't let you down? This car has been my trusty companion and is still running like a champ. It's been well-loved and is super comfortable for those daily commutes or fun weekend road trips. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and handles beautifully. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you're really going to love it!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
